---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Portugal Car Rental Booking Basics | TripAxle"
  description="Learn the booking basics for renting a car in Portugal, including insurance, deposits, card requirements, rental terms, and common mistakes."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Booking basics</p>
    <h1>Booking Basics for Renting a Car in Portugal</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Learn how insurance, card requirements, deposits, rental terms, and
      common booking mistakes can affect your Portugal car rental before you reserve.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="top-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Quick section summary</h2>
      <p>
        This section focuses on the practical details that often matter most before
        booking a rental car in Portugal.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Understand insurance and coverage options</li>
        <li>Check deposit and card requirements before booking</li>
        <li>Learn how rental terms can vary between offers</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <h2>Planned page sections</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Portugal car rental insurance explained</li>
        <li>Deposits and card requirements</li>
        <li>Broker vs direct supplier</li>
        <li>How to read rental terms before booking</li>
        <li>Common car rental mistakes in Portugal</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <article class="main-card">
      <h2>What this section will cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>How insurance and coverage options usually work</li>
        <li>What to check before booking with a credit or debit card</li>
        <li>How deposits, holds, and rental terms can vary</li>
        <li>What to double-check before finalizing a reservation</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to use this hub</h2>
      <p>
        Start here if you want to understand the rental terms behind the headline
        price. Then move to the practical guides or airport rental guides that match
        your trip.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-card">
      <h2>Related Portugal pages</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/portugal-guide">Portugal Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/airport-rental-guides">Airport Rental Guides</a></li>
        <li><a href="/practical-guides">Practical Guides</a></li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0 2.25rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #5b5b55;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .top-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card,
    .main-card,
    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e4e4de;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .side-card a {
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .top-grid,
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>